    1675 DIAGONAL Extracts diagonal from matrix or raises matrix to a power Main Index Remarks: 1.OPT = ‘COLUMN’ or ‘SQUARE’ provide exactly the same functions, except the output using COLUMN is a vector, and the output using SQUARE is a square diagonal matrix.
